QuestData.Title: Wrath of the Zandalari
QuestData.Description:
Dere is no reasoning with de mogu. Dey only value one thing: strength.
Dat is something de Zandalari have like no other, but our forces are spread thin. We are simply not prepared to fight dem.
You have proven yourself a capable warrior, for |5$r. Would you be our "ambassador" to dese brutes? Show dem dat de Zandalari do not stand alone!
QuestData.LogDescription: Slay $1oa Kao-Tien Marauders, Subjugators, or Charged Sentinels.
